<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <title>Connection Lost</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #111827;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #dc2626;
      } /* Red heading for urgency */
      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .alert-box {
        padding: 12px;
        background: #fef2f2;
        border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .platform-list {
        font-weight: bold;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        background-color: #2563eb;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <h2>Connection Lost</h2>

      <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>

      <div class='alert-box'>
        <p style='margin: 0;'>
          We have lost authorization to publish to the following platforms on
          your behalf:
        </p>
        <ul class='platform-list'>
          {{#each brokenPlatforms}}
            <li>{{this}}</li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>
        This usually happens if a password was changed, permissions were
        revoked, or the platform required a mandatory re-authentication. Any
        posts scheduled for these platforms will fail until the connection is
        restored.
      </p>

      <a href='{{integrationsUrl}}' class='button' style='color: #ffffff;'>Go to
        Integrations</a>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>© {{year}} Rooli. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>